General.Name: Pingify International Inc
General.Description: Pingify International, Inc., a development stage software technology company, focuses on the development of computer software solutions. Its solution include personal Internet notification gateway (P.I.N.G.), a two-way notification system designed to provide a user with timely and relevant information. The company was founded in 2012 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
